Detach Internet Gateway Route (15 seconds)

Scenario:
Simulates a routing misconfiguration by removing the default internet route.

What breaks:
All outbound internet access from public subnets
EC2 instances lose external connectivity

What restores:
Original route table entries are restored from S3 backup

Target:
Route Table associated with public subnet

Lambda used:
routetable_chaos

Parameters:

      TARGET_ROUTE_TABLE_ID=rtb-xxxxxxxx
      CHAOS_DURATION_SECONDS=15
      STATE_BUCKET=chaos-monkey-state-yourname

Expected behavior:
curl ifconfig.me fails during chaos
Connectivity returns after restore
